s."},{"version":"y","text":"When it is healthy, its core sticks out. Always facing the same way, it swiftly moves front to back and left to right."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Because its energy was too great to be contained, the energy leaked and formed orange crystals."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"When it is healthy, its core sticks out. Always facing the same way, it swiftly moves front to back and left to right."},{"version":"sun","text":"Its orange crystal is a mass of energy. Just one crystal fragment would provide enough fuel for a hundred dump trucks."},{"version":"moon","text":"It explores caves in search of underground water. It\u2019s not comfortable around water, so this Pok\u00e9mon takes great care in lapping it up."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"The energy overflowing from its body has turned into orange crystals that are hard enough to smash diamonds."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Its orange crystals are lumps of powerful energy. They\u2019re valuable, so Boldore is sometimes targeted for them."},{"version":"sword","text":"If you see its orange crystals start to glow, be wary. It\u2019s about to fire off bursts of energy."},{"version":"shield","text":"It relies on sound in order to monitor what\u2019s in its vicinity. When angered, it will attack without ever changing the direction it\u2019s facing."}],"evo":{"name":"roggenrola","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"boldore","level":1,"min_level":25,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"gigalith","level":2,"min_level":nu